IV. Inner Class - Data Models

1. Transaction - Represent a transaction in a Database, contain list of <tid, q, p>
---
<<private final class>>
Transaction
---
- tid : int
- q : Map<Integer, Integer>     // quantity of an item in a transaction
- p : Map<Integer, Double>      // probability of an item in a transaction
---
+ Transaction(tid, q, p)
+ getItems() : Set<Integer>             // Items is not duplicate
+ getQuantity(item : int): int          // Get quantity of an item in this transaction
+ getProbability(item : int): double    // Get probability of an item in this transaction
+ getItemCount(): int                   // Get number item in this transaction
+ toString() : String
---

